data.description:
This well maintained 3 bedroom 2 bathroom ( the second bathroom recently updated) with separate dining room home is on a large lot situated on a quiet cul-de-sac in the beautiful neighborhood of Hickory Hollow.  This oversized backyard is all fenced with a large screened porch, with plenty of space for your future swimming pool. Just relax and enjoy it with your family and friends. Home is located conveniently with just a short drive to the beaches, downtown, the Mayport Navy Base and the Mayo Clinic.  It's located close to many great restaurants, shopping and schools.  
Washer and Dryer are included as is. (good working condition)
